title: TNF Preview, Week 5 WR/CB Matchups 2022
description:
Mike Clay and Daniel Dopp preview Thursday Night Football before telling us the WR’s who NEED to be in your lineup this week and who you need to bench. Then, Adam Schefter joins to talk the storylines to watch this week including how injuries will be impacting some backfields.
